profile:
Ontario Cabinet Bed has marketed themselves as a reference point for those who seek the best solution for their rest. From natural and green friendly brands like Natura and Magniflex, organic mattress brands like Sleeptek, and the best in comfort brands like DreamStar, Ontario Cabinet Bed features a vast assortment of mattresses, Cabinet beds, Wall beds that will fit any lifestyle and budget. 

We can also customize a mattress for you if you seek a unique shape or size. 

Our Orillia location welcomes you to their shop where you can gladly try out any of our products in the showroom to find out which bed is the right solution for you.
